  "backupPrivacyWarning": "Encrypted backups (.jfwbk) require your passphrase to open. Plain JSON backups are unencrypted — store them somewhere only you can access. Restore fully replaces the data in this app — any entries you've made since the backup will be overwritten. Vision-board photos themselves aren't bundled into the backup file (only the references); if you restore on a new device, you may need to re-attach those images.",
